                "pageno" : 24,
                "suitno" : "SC.133/1995",
                "content" : "<tr><td><div>mother's lines. The accused was all right when I </div>\n\n<div>completed the treatment. But I knew that the </div>\n\n<div>ailment would re-emerge. When the accused is </div>\n\n<div>under the spell, he would not appreciate his action. </div>\n\n<div>He can't identify the action. I am not surprised that </div>\n\n<div>the accused appreciate the cause of his committing </div>\n\n<div>the murder and he revealed it to the Police that he </div>\n\n<div>did so under the control of evil spirit.\" </div>\n\n<div> </div>\n\n<div>DW3 is Mustapher Mohammed who described </div>\n\n<div>himself as a friend of the father of the appellant </div>\n\n<div>and gave the following evidence on the mental </div>\n\n<div>condition of the appellant- </div>\n\n<div>\"I know the accused. He is my friend's son. His </div>\n\n<div>father is already dead. I know DW. 1. I knew the </div>\n\n<div>DW.1 when the accused was taken to him for </div>\n\n<div>treatment for his insanity sickness. The accused </div>\n\n<div>was tied with ropes. DW.1 treated the accused. The </div>\n\n<div>accused was normal. I went there to collect the </div>\n\n<div>accused home. D.W. 1 told me that there was need </div>\n\n<div>a final treatment - apaku. I never went back </div>\n\n<div>because on his return home, he the accused was </div>\n\n<div>normal and carried on his trading business. On </div>\n\n<div>3/6/87, I did not witness the incident though I was </div>\n\n<div>at home. I was called up. I ran to the police Station </div>\n\n<div>and reported the matter to the Police.\" </div>\n\n<div> </div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">On the issue relating to the defence of insanity it </a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">has been shown through court's decisions that an </a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">accused person is not a competent witness as </a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">regards his mental status. See <i><font color=\"#5AA72D\"><b><u>Makosa v. The State </u></b></font></i></a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">(1969) 1 All NLR. 363 and <i><font color=\"#5AA72D\"><b><u>Onyekwe v. The State </u></b></font></i></a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">(1988) 1 NWLR (Pt. 72) 565. But where there is </a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">independent relevant admissible evidence </a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n\n<div>\n  <span style=\"background-color: rgb(238, 192, 1);\">\n    <a href=\"name=7270\">23 </a>\n  </span>\n</div>\n</td></tr>"
